RACE.RACE_TEXT: CANTERBURY PARK RACE 1 5F Turf CR: 88. Claiming Purse 13000. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON TWO RACES SINCE FEBRUARY 13 OR WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE MAY 13 OR WHICH HAVE NEVER WON FOUR RACES. Three Year Olds, 119 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs. Claiming Price $7,500 (Claiming Races For $6,250 Or Less Not Considered In Eligibility). Minnesota Bred Claiming Price $12,500. (If management deems it inadvisable to run this race on the Turf, it will be run at a distance of 5 Furlongs on the main track.).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: TWENTYONE N CHANGE rushed away from outset and led the field in tandem along the backstretch, took a ground saving journey around the turn, and shook clear of challenger in final sixteenth for the score. SAMURAI MIKE came away alertly and set the early pace in tandem from between rivals, was on even terms at upper stretch, but failed to match strides with eventual winner in final sixteenth. HI HO CHEERIO settled into second flight, chased the pacesetting duo around the turn from a ground saving stance, but couldnt catch the top pair in closing strides. MIAMI CROCKETT was unhurried along the backstretch, trekked the two path around the bend, and gained mildly on the leaders in final furlong. PERFECT FANNY gave chase to frontrunners along the backstretch as the widest of three abreast, maintained a wide track into the homestretch, and finished evenly. LANGUAGE BARRIER showed reserve through the opening half before passing a tiring rival in late stages. TAKE ME UP BRADY faded rapidly in the homestretch after pressing the pace from a three wide stance along the backstretch.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: ANGEL OF ATTACK pressed the early pace from a two path stance, gained command near conclusion of backstretch, had a slight advantage at upper stretch, engaged in a stretch duel and bested that rival by slimmest margin at the wire. B L'S CONCERTO trekked three wide around the opening bend, settled into a two path stance along the backstretch, and faded steadily in the latter portion of contest.
